efs.lean#L957-L974"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">theorem</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Mathlib/Data/NNReal/Defs.html#Real.nnreal_induction_on'\"><span class=\"name\">Real</span>.<span class=\"name\">nnreal_induction_on'</span></a></span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">motive</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/Data/Real/Basic.html#Real\">ℝ</a> → <a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Prop</a></span>}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">zero</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">motive</span> <span class=\"fn\">0</span></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">pos</span> : <span class=\"fn\">∀ (<span class=\"fn\">x</span> : <a href=\"./Mathlib/Data/NNReal/Defs.html#NNReal\">NNReal</a>), <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">0</span> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#LT.lt\">&lt;</a> <span class=\"fn\">x</span> → <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">motive</span> <span class=\"fn\">↑<span class=\"fn\">x</span></span></span></span></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">neg</span> : <span class=\"fn\">∀ (<span class=\"fn\">x</span> : <a href=\"./Mathlib/Data/NNReal/Defs.html#NNReal\">NNReal</a>), <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">0</span> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#LT.lt\">&lt;</a> <span class=\"fn\">x</span> → <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">motive</span> <span class=\"fn\">↑<span class=\"fn\">x</span></span></span> → <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">motive</span> (<a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Neg.neg\">-</a><span class=\"fn\">↑<span class=\"fn\">x</span></span>)</span></span></span></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">r</span> : <a href=\"./Mathlib/Data/Real/Basic.html#Real\">ℝ</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">motive</span> <span class=\"fn\">r</span></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"A version of `nnreal_induction_on` which splits into three cases (zero, positive and negative)\ninstead of two. ","docLink":"./Mathlib/Data/NNReal/Defs.html#Real.nnreal_induction_on'","kind":"theorem","line":943,"name":"Real.nnreal_induction_on'","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/0f1dd7505c3d08b5feb82300ccc73179a457bf51/Mathlib/Data/NNReal/Defs.lean#L943-L949"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">theorem</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Mathlib/Data/NNReal/Defs.html#Real.nnreal_induction_on\"><span class=\"name\">Real</span>.<span class=\"name\">nnreal_induction_on</span></a></span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">motive</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/Data/Real/Basic.html#Real\">ℝ</a> → <a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Prop</a></span>}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">nonneg</span> : <span class=\"fn\">∀ (<span class=\"fn\">x</span> : <a href=\"./Mathlib/Data/NNReal/Defs.html#NNReal\">NNReal</a>), <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">motive</span> <span class=\"fn\">↑<span class=\"fn\">x</span></span></span></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">nonpos</span> : <span class=\"fn\">∀ (<span class=\"fn\">x</span> : <a href=\"./Mathlib/Data/NNReal/Defs.html#NNReal\">NNReal</a>), <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">motive</span> <span class=\"fn\">↑<span class=\"fn\">x</span></span></span> → <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">motive</span> (<a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Neg.neg\">-</a><span class=\"fn\">↑<span class=\"fn\">x</span></span>)</span></span></span>)</span></s